OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSara Pascoe revealed as new
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FGreat British Sewing Bee   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhost                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Comic and writer Sara Pascoe is to take
OL,6, on hosting duties for The Great British
OL,7, Sewing Bee from Joe Lycett, who has    
OL,8, stepped down after three series.       
OL,10,FShe will join judges Patrick Grant and 
OL,11,FEsme Young when the show, which tries  
OL,12,Fto find the UK's best amateur sewer,   
OL,13,Freturns to BBC One next year.          
OL,15,FPascoe, who appeared as a contestant on
OL,16,Fthe show's 2020 Christmas celebrity    
OL,17,Fspecial, said it was "such an honour". 
OL,19,FLycett said he was "absolutely         
OL,20,Fthrilled" his friend was the new host. 
